text: Echinovelleda antiqua is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Gressitt in 1951. It is known from China.BioLib.cz - Echinovelleda antiqua. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Phrissomini Category:Beetles described in 1951
title: Echinovelleda antiqua
